Classes:

User abstract class
 + name, email, abstract postMessage() (blockUser())
AdminUser implements Administration, Moderation
ModUser implements Moderation
RegularUser implements Reportable

Post implements Reportable, Likable
 + user, msg, timestamp, likers, reported, moderated, accepted

PostBoard implements Reportable
 + subject, posts 
ReportedPost extends Post
 + post, reporters, status, moderator
ReportedUser extends User
 + reporters, status, moderator
ReportedBoard extends PostBoard
 + reporters, status, moderator


Network
 + reportPosts, reportUser, reportedBoards


Interfaces:

Likeable interface
 + like(), unlike()
Reportable inteface
 + report(),
Moderation inteface
 + viewReportInbox(), deleteMessage()
Administration interface
 + deleteUser(), banUser()
